<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>聖イジー教会。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>有料のお土産エリアでブックマークを購入。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>拷問用の塔があった。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>坂を下る。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>プラハの公衆トイレはすべて有料。1ユーロ。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>昼飯。</p>

<pre class="address">
Naše maso
Dlouhá 727/39, 110 00 Staré Město, Czech
</pre>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>精肉屋の片隅で食べる半生ハンバーグと、温かいパストラミサンド。ビールは自分でつぐスタイル。どっちも美味い。765チェコクローネ。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>世界一周最後の晩飯は、観光エリアから出てみた。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>晩飯。</p>

<pre class="address">
Pivnice u Járy
Dalimilova 1, 130 00 Praha 3-Žižkov, Czech
</pre>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>Kamenice。少人数で回してる店なのでビール飲みながらのんびり待つ。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>Tradiční hovězí svíčková na smetaně shouskovým knedlikem, brusinky(伝統料理)とソーセージのグリル。ビールはVilem。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>追加で馬鹿メシ。揚げたチーズにタルタルソース。Vilemをさらにお代わりして合計でチップ入れて938チェココロナ。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>腹パンパン。バスで戻る。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="video swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>
]]></description>
        <dc:date>2026-2026-04T00:00:00+09:00</dc:date>

  </item>
  <item rdf:about="2026/0419-prague/">
            <title>2026/04/19: 世界一周旅行 その30 チェコ</title>
        <link>https://www.don.to/diary/2026/0419-prague/</link>
        <description><![CDATA[<p>宿の朝食。チーズ美味い。ソーセージ美味い。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>カフカの像。一時間に一回、回転する。超ショボい。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="video swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>Mucha美術館。19世紀の画家。イラストレーターの走りですね。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>天文時計。これも一時間に一回のイベント。ショボい。
正面から見ると、上部の稼働部がもうちょっと見えるらしい。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="video swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>旧市街広場。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>聖ミクラーシュ教会。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>昼食。</p>

<pre class="address">
Lokál Dlouhááá
Dlouhá 33, 110 00 Staré Město, Czech
</pre>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>ここも飲んだビールがカウントされるスタイル。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>牛生肉のタルタルと揚げたパン。美味い。ビール2杯と炭酸水飲んで合計514チェココロナ。</p>

<p>生ニンニク齧って殺菌や！と思ってたら、パンに擦り付けるらしい。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>路面電車に乗る。30分乗り放題で39チェココロナ。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>Chotek Gardensから街並みを見る。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>クラーロヴスカー庭園から、聖ヴィート大聖堂の裏側を見る。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>レトナ公園を歩いて街に戻る。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<pre class="address">
<a href="https://www.udvouvelbloudu.cz/">Restaurace U Dvou velbloudů</a>
Kožná 474/4, 110 00 Staré Město, Czech
</pre>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p><a href="https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E3%83%90%E3%83%89%E3%83%AF%E3%82%A4%E3%82%B6%E3%83%BC#%E5%90%8D%E7%A7%B0%E3%82%92%E3%82%81%E3%81%90%E3%82%8B%E7%B4%9B%E4%BA%89">本家バドワイザー</a>。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>ノンアルコール版。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>豚の膝(1kg)。1kgといっても骨の部分もあるが、二人でも結構お腹いっぱい。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>バドワイザー(Budvar)のダーク。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>お代はチップ入れて900チェココルナ。</p>

<p>夜のカレル橋とモルダウ川(ヴルタヴァ川)。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
