  <item rdf:about="2026/0418-prague/">
            <title>2026/04/18: 世界一周旅行 その29 ギリシャ → チェコ</title>
        <link>https://www.don.to/diary/2026/0418-prague/</link>
        <description><![CDATA[<p>昨日買っておいたプラムを食べた後、宿の無料パウンドケーキをつまみつつ、アクロポリス遺跡へ。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>今日はアクロポリス遺跡が<a href="http://odysseus.culture.gr/h/3/eh355.jsp?obj_id=2384">無料で見学</a>できる日。オープン前から並ぶ。無料チケットを発券してもらって入場。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>ディオニソス劇場。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>アテナ古神殿。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>パルテノン神殿。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>露天のイチゴを買う。2ユーロ。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>宿に戻ってチェックアウト。まだ時間あるので共用エリアで時間潰す。</p>

<p>ファラフェル(3.8ユーロ)をテイクアウトして、イチゴと一緒に食べる。</p>

<pre class="address">
Falafellas
Aiolou 51, Athina 105 51, Greece
</pre>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>空港へ移動。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>ラウンジへ。トルコでは弱小だったAegan Airlineもギリシャでは最強。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>サラダがバカうま。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>最後の都市、プラハに向かいます。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>Tsipouroというローカル蒸留酒をいただく。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>ヨーロッパっぽい、街と街が緑が区切られた景色になってきた。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>無骨な都市構造。共産主義の名残りかしら。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>プラハ到着。飛行機から降りた途端にパスポートチェックをくらう。
EU内移動なので、この後は何もなし。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>空港の両替所は超ぼったくり。結局、最後までチェコクローネの現金は不要だった。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>最後の都市でやっとトイレットペーパーを流せるわー。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>バスとメトロ共通の乗車券を買う。30分乗り放題。クレカで買えた。39チェココロナ。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>バスとメトロを乗り継いで旧市街へ。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>Muster駅。ヨーロッパの街並みだ。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>今回の宿。</p>

<pre class="address">
Hotel Jungmann
Jungmannovo nám. 762/2, 110 00 Nové Město, Czech
</pre>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>町をブラつく。久しぶりのヨーロッパらしいヨーロッパに感動している。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>カレル橋。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>お腹一杯なのでビールだけ飲みにきた。蒸留所併設のビアレストラン。</p>

<pre class="address">
Restaurace a pivovar U Fleků
Křemencova 11, 110 00 Nové Město, Czech
</pre>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>ビールが美味い！さすがチェコ。飲んだ杯数だけ線が引かれるスタイル</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>ビールはテーブルまで押し売りが来る。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>音楽も押し売り。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="video swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>カードが使えないと言われて焦るが、ユーロの現金払いでもOKだった。助かった。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>WeWorkあった。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>
]]></description>
        <dc:date>2026-2026-04T00:00:00+09:00</dc:date>

  </item>
  <item rdf:about="2026/0417-greece/">
            <title>2026/04/17: 世界一周旅行 その28 ギリシャ</title>
        <link>https://www.don.to/diary/2026/0417-greece/</link>
        <description><![CDATA[<p>宿の共有スペース。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>マーケットへ。肉エリアと鮮魚エリアで分かれてる。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>遺跡散歩。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>坂を登って見晴らしのいいエリアへ。アテネという街があってね。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="video swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>鳥。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>通りすがりの猫にからむ。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>下る。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>朝食。牛肉のピタ。二人で7ユーロ。</p>

<pre class="address">
Kosta
Pl. Agias Irinis 2, Athina 105 60, Greece
</pre>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>スーパーをチェック。
コーラよりビールが安い。節約のためにはしょうがない</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>お前ギリシャにもおったんか。トルコとギリシャって色々似ているのね。海挟んで隣りだもんなあ。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>コーヒー休憩。</p>

<pre class="address">
Apollonos cafe
Apollonos 28, Athina 105 56, Greece
</pre>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>ゼウス神殿へ向かう。改装中。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>ギリシャもトイレは便座レス。空気椅子状態で用を足すらしい。毎日スクワット。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>昼飯。</p>

<pre class="address">
Taverna Saita
Kidathineon 21, Athina 105 58, Greece
</pre>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>イカのグリルと塩鱈のフライ。ビールと水で34ユーロ。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>ミトロポレオス大聖堂。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>オーガニック系のスーパーも覗く。
ヒツジとヤギのプロテイン？何で混ぜた。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>Panagía Kapnikaréa Church。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>宿のエレベーターはすげえ旧式で外扉は手で開けるタイプ。不安になるくらい遅い。エヴァ22話ぐらい</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="video swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>夕焼けを見に行く。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="video swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>雲が出てきたので夕焼け見れそうにないので、下る。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>晩飯。</p>

<pre class="address">
Ο Θανάσης
Mitropoleos 69, Athina 105 55, Greece
</pre>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>Greekサラダ、ヨーグルトケバブ。ピルスナー。チップ入れて33ユーロ。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>
]]></description>
        <dc:date>2026-2026-04T00:00:00+09:00</dc:date>

  </item>
  <item rdf:about="2026/0416-greece/">
            <title>2026/04/16: 世界一周旅行 その27 ギリシャ</title>
        <link>https://www.don.to/diary/2026/0416-greece/</link>
        <description><![CDATA[<p>宿のご主人の計らいで、8時前に朝食を軽くいただいてから、手配された空港行きの乗り合いシャトルバスに乗り、Navensir空港へ。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>空港のトイレには、中華式便座があった。当惑する欧米人。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>イスタンブールへ。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>イスタンブール着。トルコ航空が空港のいい場所を全て占拠している。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>トルコ航空のビジネスクラスカウンターすげえ。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>我々は今回はAegan Airlinesなので、トルコ的には弱小航空会社。その他大勢のエリアに行って、チェックインカウンターが開くのをじっと待つ。
トルコ航空なら四六時中カウンター開いてるんですけどね。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>やっとスタッフが来て、チェックイン始まったと思ったら、システム障害ぽくてひたすら列で待つ。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>テンパる責任者。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>この後、チェックインカウンターが2回変わってウロウロさせられた後、ようやく発券に成功。
フライトがややこしいので紙発券しかしてこなかったけど、オンラインチェックインした方がよかったかもしれない(結果論)。</p>

<p>ラウンジはイスタンブール航空のものが使える。すげえ豪華。
3時間以上滞在するつもりだったけど、1時間ぐらいしか滞在できない。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>Rakiという蒸留酒を試したかったがワインしかなかった。
EFESとスパークリングワインをざくろジュースで割って飲む。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>料理を目の前で調理して、よそってくれるんだけど、供給が追いついてない。
一番混んでるケバブは食えんかった</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>アテネに向かいます。責任者はこっちにも来てて、搭乗手続きとドアクローズもやってた。忙しい。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>Ouzoという蒸留酒を試す。水割り、強い上にクセが強い。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>Aeganって読み方すら分からなかったけど、エーゲ海の「エーゲ」か！</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>アテネ着。
EU版ESTAの準備してる。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>メトロで市内へ。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>Μοναστηράκι駅着。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>今日の宿。4人部屋のドミトリー。</p>

<pre class="address">
<a href="http://bedbox.gr/">Bedbox Athens</a>
Polykleitou 11, Athina 105 51, Greece
</pre>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>近所のコインランドリーで溜まった洗濯物を洗う。
この機械、お釣りが出てくる！</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>まだ時間が早いので一杯飲みに行くかと出かけたが、付近にいい店が見当たらなかったので、路上の売店でギリシャビールを買ってきて、テラスで晩酌。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>
]]></description>
        <dc:date>2026-2026-04T00:00:00+09:00</dc:date>

  </item>
  <item rdf:about="2026/0415-nevsehir/">
            <title>2026/04/15: 世界一周旅行 その26 トルコ (カッパドキア)</title>
        <link>https://www.don.to/diary/2026/0415-nevsehir/</link>
        <description><![CDATA[<p>宿で朝食。窓には気球が見える。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>自転車を借りて(40ユーロ)散策。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>秘宝館。英語名もLove Valleyなので、みんな考えることは一緒やな。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>戻ります。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>宿に戻って休憩して、Red Valleyへ向かうつもりが急坂過ぎてギブアップ。
途中の見晴らしスポットに寄って戻る。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>休憩して、今度は夕焼けを見にRose Valley。
天気予報は微妙。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="video swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="video swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>なかなか陽が沈まないので、最寄りの野外コーヒー屋へ。観光地値段の上、全く美味しくない。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>映え写真を撮ってる人がいた。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>雲が増えたので夕焼けは諦める。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="video swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>スーパーでティーパックをチェック。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>晩飯。</p>

<pre class="address">
Smoky Kebap & Steak Restaurant
İsali - Gaferli - Avcılar, Müze Cd. 42/4, 50180 Göreme/Nevşehir Merkez/Nevşehir, Turkey
</pre>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>Mixedケバブと、鉄板フンモス。暖かいフンモスを初めて食べた。うまい。ビール3本飲んで3490トルコリラ。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>猫の店長もいた。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>ミャクミャク風の魔除けを購入。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>
]]></description>
        <dc:date>2026-2026-04T00:00:00+09:00</dc:date>

  </item>
  <item rdf:about="2026/0414-nevsehir/">
            <title>2026/04/14: 世界一周旅行 その25 トルコ (カッパドキア)</title>
        <link>https://www.don.to/diary/2026/0414-nevsehir/</link>
        <description><![CDATA[<p>部屋前のテラス。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>早朝散歩。眺めのいいところにいくのに二人で60トルコリラのお布施。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a></p>

<p>気球を眺める。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="video swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe"><img src="/images/under.webp" height="96" alt="" /></a>
